aa(lp13
VIf you had asked me 10 years ago whether or not
p14
aVwe would ever be able to sequence the genome of extinct animals,
p15
aVI would have told you, it's unlikely.
p16
aVIf you had asked whether or not we would actually be able
p17
aVto revive an extinct species,
p18
aVI would have said, pipe dream.
