aVbut the revival of an extinct species is actually within reach,
p23
aVmaybe not from the insects in amber \u2014
p24
aVin fact, this mosquito was actually used
p25
aVfor the inspiration for "Jurassic Park" \u2014
p26
aVbut from woolly mammoths, the well preserved remains
p27
aVof woolly mammoths in the permafrost.
